data.description: Hidden gem! This corner villa offers lots of flexibility with an open floor plan, split bedroom layout, 8' doors with 9' ceilings, new maintenance-free LVT throughout and one car garage in highly-desirable North Naples.  The Tuscan design offers barrel tile roof, private paver walkway and paver driveway.  Close to new shopping and restaurants at Founders Square, just off of Collier Blvd and Immokalee.  The gated community offers luxury amenities including resort-style pool and hot tub, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis and basketball courts, playground and community park. Freshly painted interior and exterior.
